summary: This is an ENB based off my own personal taste going for a fantasy look. Uses high quality SSAO, bokeh DOF, intense god rays, and Matso's bloom code. Days are bright and colorful, while nights and dungeons are dark but not overly dark like most mods I've found.
descriptionHtml:
Features:
-Bright colorful days!
-Bright blue skies!
-Nights are dark but not too dark
-Intense God Rays
-SSAO
-Detailed Shadows
-Skylighting
-DOF with auto-focus(thanks to gp65cj04 for code!)
-Matso's Bloom code
-HD6 by HeliosDoubleSix

Mods Compatible:
I'm still messing with settings for other mods and I will release presets based on feedback. If you use any lighting/weather mods and it works fine with this preset let me know what mod you're using. As of right now I know that these mods work.
Further Darker Dungeons for ENB
Revamped Exterior Fog
Dark Lights Template
Climates of Tamriel(appears to work fine)

Mods I heavily suggest you use:
More Subtle Nirnroots- No Glow(DOWNLOAD THIS!)
Remove Ambient Interior Fog(DOWNLOAD THIS!)

Mods Recommended:
Lanterns of Skyrim
Light Up The Night- People Carry Torches
Claralux- More and Brighter Lights
Better Embers
SMAA
Psyrim
author: TheRainbow
